# Feishu Bridge Configuration
# IMPORTANT: Create a NEW independent Feishu app for this bridge.
# Do NOT reuse cli_a92d11a974b89bcd (mi-feishu MCP app) — event routing will conflict.
# See: https://open.feishu.cn/app to create a new app with im:message permissions.
